	  <div id="side"> <!-- Block of text on left side of page -->
	    <div style="text-align: center">JMRI&reg; is...</div>
	    <dl>
		<dt><h3><a href="./apps/DecoderPro">DecoderPro&reg;</a></h3></dt>
		<dd>
		    A better tool for programming decoders.
		    DecoderPro simplifies the job of configuring complicated DCC decoders
		    by providing screens on which you can select the various options and
		    values you want.
		</dd>

		<dt><h3><a href="./apps/PanelPro/PanelPro.html">PanelPro&trade;</a></h3></dt>
		<dd>
		    Designing and Operating CRT based CTC control panels that reflect the real-time
		    state of your railroad <em>and</em> let you control it - almost like
		    a Prototype dispatcher!
		</dd>

		<dt><h3><a href="./tools/index.shtml">General Tools</a></h3></dt>
		<dd>JMRI provides powerful tools for working with your
		layout.
		    <UL>
		    <LI><dfn><a href="tools/throttle/ThrottleMain.html">Throttles</a></dfn>
		    <LI><dfn><a href="tools/ConsistTool/ConsistTool.html">Consisting</a></dfn>
		    <LI><dfn><a href="tools/Lights.html">Lights</a></dfn>
		    <LI><dfn><a href="tools/Routes.html">Routes</a></dfn>
		    <LI><dfn><a href="tools/Logix.html">Logix</a></dfn>
		    <LI><dfn><a href="tools/fastclock">Fast Clocks</a>
		    <LI><dfn><a href="apps/Speedometer/index.html">Speedometer</a> &amp;<BR>
		    <a href="help/en/html/tools/speedometer/SpeedMatch.shtml">Engine Speed Matching</a></dfn>
		    <LI><dfn><a href="doc/scripts/index.html">Scripting</a></dfn>
		    <LI><dfn><a href="hardware/PDA.html">PDA access</a></dfn>
		    <LI><dfn><a href="apps/LocoTools">LocoNet tools</a></dfn>
		    </UL>
		</dd>

		<dt><h3><a href="./apps/Automation">Layout Automation</a></h3></dt>
		<dd>JMRI can be used to automate parts 
		of your layout, from simply controlling a crossing gate
		to running trains in the background.
		    <UL>
		    <LI><dfn><a href="./apps/Signalling">Signaling</a></dfn>
		    <LI><dfn><a href="doc/scripts/index.html">Scripting</a></dfn>
		    </UL>
		</dd>

		<div style="clear: both"></div>
